headline.main: Exclusive-EBRD to Return to Uzbekistan After Decade-Long Absence
headline.print_headline: Exclusive-EBRD to Return to Uzbekistan After Decade-Long Absence

lead_paragraph: The European Bank for Reconstruction and Development will this week signal it is to ready to restart work in Uzbekistan after a decade-long absence, sources at the bank have told Reuters.
